name: Docket To-do App
description:
This file contains trail versions of onboarding, signing up, and creating a task flow (assign user, schedule, and set priority), as well as a calendar and preferences UI screens. A separate page containing a components library and a styleguide is included in the file, in addition to the UI screens.


The UI flows include Onboarding, Homescreen, Creating a Task, Calendar View & Profile
